00:01:48.737 --> 00:01:52.106
UNK in Shavl dort iz do a geto, zogt er, veys ikh hundert protsent.

00:01:52.230 --> 00:01:53.692
vayle er flegt oyf di merk,

00:01:54.019 --> 00:01:55.835
