00:02:03.300 --> 00:02:06.905
un hobn mir zikh opgeredn tsu trefn dray kilometer hintern shtetl, oyf shavler veg.

00:02:07.553 --> 00:02:09.690
un ikh bin genumen un ferd,

00:02:09.797 --> 00:02:13.081
un ikh bin geforn, un m'iz durkhgeforn tsvey postes, di daytshn.

00:02:13.442 --> 00:02:14.836
