dortn fun dray kroyt geven.

00:11:32.562 --> 00:11:36.302
nu mir vartn ven m'vet zey firn shisn. ikh hobn shoyn gehat vos ontsuvern, veystu dokh.

00:11:37.557 --> 00:11:38.920
un m'hot nokh arestirt

00:11:38.920 --> 00:11:40.287
Zisl Shvarts,

00:11:40.287 --> 00:11:41.617
vu mir zaynen gelebt bay im,

00:11:42.366 --> 00:11:46.072
oykh arayngefaln dort. un er hot grade a kind nebekh, di froy iz im aynge⟨UNK⟩.

00:11:46.585 --> 00:11:51.827
un er hot geveynt in turme un gebetn bay got. got, zogt er, helf mayne kinderlekh, zogt er, zaynen in geto, zogt er.

00:11:52.103 --> 00:11:56.231
zoln nit zayn hungerik, zogt er, ikh trog zey dokh arayn altsding, un er hot getrogn a bisl mel.

00:11:57.013 --> 00:12:02.997
andere hobn getrogn dortn, oykh dortn ikh veys nit vos, a shtikl puter aza tsvey hundert gram, hot eyner UNK arestirt.

00:12:03.578 --> 00:12:06.829
ikh hob, mayne broyt iz geven in gantsn dort fir hundert gram.

00:12:10.024 --> 00:12:11.118
dos glaykh

00:12:11.118 --> 00:12:12.819
iz do alts nisim fun eybershtn.

00:12:12.842 --> 00:12:16.261
eyner fun undzere arestirte, fun fun di tsvelf mentshn,

00:12:16.960 --> 00:12:18.810
iz geven zeyer a a raykher yat,

00:12:19.153 --> 00:12:24.817
hobn di eltern oysgekoyft, tsuge- tsugegangen tsum gebits-komisar, m'hot im gegebn di brilyantene zakhn,

00:12:25.026 --> 00:12:26.505
un m'hot im aroysgelozn.

00:12:26.697 --> 00:12:29.036
heyst es, zey hobn geshonken, hot men alemen undz geshonken.

00:12:29.667 --> 00:12:36.799
hot men tsamgerufn beyde, in Shavl iz geven tsvey getos, Kavkaze un Trako, ikh bin nit in Kavka- in Trako geto, in in Kavkazer geto bin ikh geven.

00:12:37.260 --> 00:12:41.101
un m'hot tsamgerufn oyf a plats, a leydikn plats, fun beyde getos di mentshn,

00:12:43.116 --> 00:12:45.894
un m'hot bashlosn tsu gebn alemen finf un tsvontsik shmits,

00:12:46.440 --> 00:12:47.801
geleygt oyf di tishn.

00:12:48.432 --> 00:12:49.846
geven a langer tish,

00:12:49.846 --> 00:12:55.816
un der Gebits-Komisar iz geshtanen, un ale, nokh daytshn geven un di litviner, un m'hot alemen geharget finf un tsvontsik shmits.

00:12:56.262 --> 00:12:57.977
geshtanen an elterer yid,

00:12:58.185 --> 00:13:01.233
ikh gedenk gut im, mit a langn bord,

00:13:01.662 --> 00:13:03.023
un ikh bin shoyn geven,

00:13:03.028 --> 00:13:05.367
geshtanen der der naynter oder der tsenter,

00:13:05.458 --> 00:13:06.498
tsu krign.

00:13:06.876 --> 00:13:09.857
dem yingl zogt er, dem yingl zogt er, veln zey avekhargenen.

00:13:10.960 --> 00:13:14.323
ober zey hobn zikh shoyn ongefresn, ongegesn zikh mit di mit di

00:13:14.323 --> 00:13:18.868
mit di dos vos zey hobn geharget shoyn di akh- di nayn mentshn,

00:13:19.178 --> 00:13:20.204
di akht mentshn,

00:13:20.204 --> 00:13:23.779
iz zey shoyn geven gut oyfn hartsn az zey hobn shoyn di yidn geharget un gehat hanoe fun derayn,

00:13:24.915 --> 00:13:27.356
hot der yid mikh gegebn a tsi arayn,

00:13:28.375 --> 00:13:29.966
tsvishn di geshtanene mentshn,

00:13:29.966 --> 00:13:32.452
un ikh bin oysge- oysgemitn di hargeray.

00:13:32.712 --> 00:13:34.461
hob ikh nit gekrogn di hargeray.

00:13:40.103 --> 00:13:46.020
di gantse epizodn fun geto iz shver tsu dertseyln, ikh vel nor aykh derts- ikh ken nor dertseyln vos iz forgekumen azayne min tragedishe zakhn.

00:13:49.570 --> 00:13:53.732
day- di shavler getos hobn gehat filyaln arum k- arum Shavl,

00:13:54.143 --> 00:13:55.338
tsigl-fabrik,

00:13:55.338 --> 00:13:56.392
tsuker fabrik,

00:13:56.392 --> 00:13:57.377
un torf,

00:13:57.703 --> 00:13:59.387
oystsuarbetn di torg dortn.

00:13:59.387 --> 00:14:03.050
flegt men undz oyf zumer avekfirn dortn arbetn fun

00:14:03.050 --> 00:14:04.633
makhn dortn azane min

00:14:05.078 --> 00:14:07.957
shtiblekh tsaytvaylike hobn dort gehaltn.

00:14:07.963 --> 00:14:10.677
un mir flegn dortn, ikh bin geven a gantsn shoyn,

00:14:10.677 --> 00:14:14.167
a gantsn zumer baym grobn der di di torf fun di ⟨radvilersik⟩,

00:14:14.680 --> 00:14:15.872
mit Kalmenen,

00:14:16.688 --> 00:14:18.639
vayle Kalmen fun in ergets nit oplozn.

00:14:19.101 --> 00:14:20.985
un nokh dem flegt er shoyn zayn nor mit mir,

00:14:22.138 --> 00:14:24.072
zogt er, zey veln dir umbrengen, zogt er dortn.

00:14:24.754 --> 00:14:29.000
un nokh dem hot men undz gemakht in geto hot men undz avekgefirt

00:14:29.378 --> 00:14:31.650
in fabrik, in tsuker fabrik.

00:14:31.977 --> 00:14:34.201
dos in dray un draysi- in dray un fertsikstn yor

00:14:34.201 --> 00:14:35.481
iz forgekumen der mayse.

00:14:37.579 --> 00:14:39.429
un dortn bin ikh krank gevorn

00:14:39.705 --> 00:14:46.567
oyf tif. hot men gezogt dem lager firer

00:14:47.907 --> 00:14:49.234
fun tsuker fabrik.

00:14:49.375 --> 00:14:52.356
a a lit- a litviner? a yid? a daytsh?

00:14:51.720 --> 00:14:54.299
a daytsh, UNK dos iz geven di daytshn.

00:14:54.299 --> 00:14:55.716
gehit hobn undz di

00:14:55.716 --> 00:14:58.307
di di ukrainer

00:14:58.307 --> 00:15:00.574
vos hobn zikh far- farkoyft far di daytshn.

00:15:03.415 --> 00:15:04.928
un etlekhe litviner.

00:15:06.030 --> 00:15:08.218
un grade in dem tsuker fabrik,

00:15:08.680 --> 00:15:09.889
vos hot undz gehit,

00:15:09.928 --> 00:15:12.132
iz geven Raskausker's a tsveyter zun.

00:15:13.624 --> 00:15:14.799
als a shoymer?

00:15:14.620 --> 00:15:16.993
ye, er hot gesh- geshosn yidn.

00:15:17.033 --> 00:15:18.832
Kalmen iz avekgegangen,

00:15:20.121 --> 00:15:22.899
aroysgegangen durkh di drotn dortn tsu brengen sh-

00:15:23.648 --> 00:15:25.130
esn, er hot genumen bay yidn z-

00:15:25.130 --> 00:15:28.215
zakhn oystsubaytn, mir hobn keyn zakhn dokh nit gehat, di yidn hobn gehat nokh zakhn.

00:15:28.795 --> 00:15:32.062
un er hot im gekhapt arayngeyendik, ot der Bakazimerers,

00:15:32.119 --> 00:15:33.412
Raskausker's zun,

00:15:34.060 --> 00:15:36.045
zogt er, der mol, zogt er, shenk ikh dir,

00:15:36.658 --> 00:15:39.672
der tsveyter mo, zogt er, vel ikh dir opshisn vi m'hot opgeshosn dayne brider.

00:15:40.692 --> 00:15:42.863
Kalmen, hot dos dertseylt, zog ikh, Kalmen, mer zolstu nit geyn.

00:15:43.577 --> 00:15:48.397
geyn nit mer, zog ikh, mir veln esn broyt mit zalts, zogt er, er geyt nit, zog ikh, gey nit, UNK, iz er nit gegangen.

00:15:48.994 --> 00:15:49.961
hot men mir

00:15:49.961 --> 00:15:51.991
avekgefirt heys dos in Shavler,

00:15:54.597 --> 00:15:55.806
in ge- der,

00:15:56.082 --> 00:15:58.314
in Shavler geto iz geven mitn

00:15:58.314 --> 00:16:00.851
mitn besoylem iz er tsamgegangen.

00:16:01.448 --> 00:16:05.610
un oyfn besoylem iz geven di tare-shtibl fun shov- fun kovnever, fun shavler yidn.

00:16:05.633 --> 00:16:07.095
hot men dortn gemakht

00:16:07.135 --> 00:16:09.199
dem krankn-hoyz far di yidn.

00:16:09.199 --> 00:16:11.398
vayl di be- far di yidn fun shavler geto.

00:16:12.214 --> 00:16:15.076
un m'hot mir gezogt az ikh bin krank gevorn oyf lungen-ontsindung.

00:16:15.302 --> 00:16:17.220
ven oyf tif iz dokh nito vos tsum redn.

00:16:17.007 --> 00:16:18.435
volt men aykh nisht genumen.

00:16:18.002 --> 00:16:20.679
volt men oyfn ort opgefa- opgeshosn.

00:16:21.327 --> 00:16:22.755
hot men mir avekgefirt

00:16:23.588 --> 00:16:25.910
in besoylem un di yidishe

00:16:26.592 --> 00:16:29.589
hobn gevust az ikh bin krank oyf tif, dortn geven doktoyrim,

00:16:30.490 --> 00:16:33.420
Dokter Peshekhovitsh gefint zikh in Erets- in Amerike,

00:16:34.202 --> 00:16:38.213
vos hot mir geratevet dem lebn dortn.

00:16:39.214 --> 00:16:49.232
bist a yunger yingl, zogt er, di, zogt er, mir hobn do nit azoy fil, zogt er, di refues, zogt er, dir tsu rateven, zogt er, un ikh vel krign bay di litviner, zogt er, in shtot, un ikh vel dir, zogt er, helfn vel ikh kenen, ot dos.

00:16:53.389 --> 00:16:54.812
vos iz forgekumen

00:16:54.812 --> 00:16:57.095
az ikh bin gelegn bin ikh shoyn geven kimat geven gezunt.

00:17:03.531 --> 00:17:05.280
mit mir iz gelegn nokh a meydl,

00:17:05.353 --> 00:17:06.911
ot dem Shek's bruder,

00:17:06.911 --> 00:17:08.637
vos iz do haynt in Kovne, Shek,

00:17:09.336 --> 00:17:11.439
un di meydl iz geven zayne a kale.

00:17:11.917 --> 00:17:16.673
a- zi iz gelegn oyf tif, ober fun ir iz geven a m- zeyer shver di mayse.

00:17:16.673 --> 00:17:20.889
zi hot gemakht zikh do koyln un di koyln zenen gevorn ⟨guzes⟩.

00:17:23.089 --> 00:17:26.120
un in der moment hot men gemakht di kinder aktsye in Shavl.

00:17:27.138 --> 00:17:29.343
dos iz shoyn geven shoyn ende dray un fertsik take?

00:17:28.945 --> 00:17:31.234
ya, ende dray un fertsik iz dos geven.

00:17:33.079 --> 00:17:36.785
hob ikh gelegn nokh mit eynem Yosken, a linkuver yat, Yoske Gurye.

00:17:37.095 --> 00:17:39.232
a linkuver yat un er lebt itster in Kanade.

00:17:39.542 --> 00:17:41.223
er iz geven elter mit mir in tsvey yor.

00:17:42.343 --> 00:17:43.737
oykh antlofn fun shisn.

00:17:44.098 --> 00:17:45.256
fun Linkuva shisn.

00:17:46.562 --> 00:17:48.294
zogt er, Khatskl, zogt er mir,

00:17:48.368 --> 00:17:49.813
UNK zogt er,

00:17:50.325 --> 00:17:53.477
zogt er, der personal, di doktoyrim, di krankn-shvester, zogt er,

00:17:53.477 --> 00:17:56.574
epes gefelt mir nit, zogt er, zey loyfn arum do haynt, zogt er

00:17:56.574 --> 00:17:59.854
vi es kumt do for azanen, zogt er. zog ikh, Yoske, un ver veynt do?

00:18:00.822 --> 00:18:03.431
m'veynt! du herst nit? zog ikh, m'veynt! kinder veynen!

00:18:04.551 --> 00:18:06.317
oyber azoy vi s'forgekumen

00:18:08.365 --> 00:18:11.464
di veg vos iz gegangen tsum vokzaln fun geto,

00:18:12.010 --> 00:18:13.033
iz lebn

00:18:13.326 --> 00:18:16.070
BOLNICHNYY undzer, lebn krankn-hoyz,

00:18:16.228 --> 00:18:17.035
hot zey,

00:18:17.035 --> 00:18:19.041
flegn, az m'hot gefirt di kinder,

00:18:20.532 --> 00:18:22.433
in di ⟨gruzevikes⟩,

00:18:22.202 --> 00:18:23.681
in di UNK?

00:18:23.299 --> 00:18:24.440
hobn zey geveynt.

00:18:25.054 --> 00:18:27.411
in der in di oytomobiln farmakhte.

00:18:27.552 --> 00:18:32.119
hobn zey geveynt un geshrien! der mame, der tate, der altsding. ze'mir aroysgekumen oyf UNK,

00:18:32.361 --> 00:18:33.637
m'firt di kinder.

00:18:35.500 --> 00:18:37.859
zogt Yoske, zogt er tsu mir, Khatskl, lomir, zogt er, aroys.

00:18:37.859 --> 00:18:39.521
lomir, zogt er, antloyfn fun danet.

00:18:39.521 --> 00:18:41.737
zog ikh, Yoske, mir hobn dokh keyn zakh nit, zogt er,

00:18:42.115 --> 00:18:45.382
un di doktoyrim, di ⟨krankeshn⟩, hobn zikh ale aropgenumen zikh fun dortn.

00:18:45.962 --> 00:18:50.900
avek fun di geto, fun ba- fun krankn-hoyz avekgegangen, un undz alem ibergelozn do.

00:18:51.042 --> 00:18:55.457
un Yoske hot ongefangen zukhn, un gefunen zeyere zakhn, un mir hobn zikh ongeton mit Yosken di zakhn,

00:18:56.053 --> 00:18:59.540
un mir zaynen avekgegangen oyfn besoylem iz geven fun di rabonim di shtiblekh,

00:19:00.019 --> 00:19:01.717
hobn mir zikh arayngeleygt in a shtibl, beyde.

00:19:03.293 --> 00:19:04.434
un mir zaynen gelegn.

00:19:04.879 --> 00:19:07.876
un di aktsyes fun di kinder iz forgekumen a- biz a halber nakht.

00:19:08.271 --> 00:19:10.745
zenen mir tsugegangen, ot der besoylem iz geven arumgetsamt

00:19:10.988 --> 00:19:12.197
mit a tsam

00:19:13.468 --> 00:19:15.959
fun tsement, mit tsi- mit mit mit shteyner.

00:19:16.641 --> 00:19:18.002
ober s'geven lekher.

00:19:18.818 --> 00:19:21.292
az m'iz tsu tsugegangen mit im bay nakht kukn di lekher mi-

00:19:21.298 --> 00:19:22.254
vos mir hobn,

00:19:22.260 --> 00:19:26.017
Yoske iz nokh aroysgekrokhn, zogt er, do blayb ikh, er iz geven in gantsn,

00:19:26.766 --> 00:19:28.228
er iz geven a blonder.

00:19:28.791 --> 00:19:30.827
er iz geven punkt azoy vi litviner oysgezen.

00:19:31.660 --> 00:19:36.128
iz er aroysgekrokhn, zogt er, Khatske, zogt er, m'firt di kinder, zogt er. m'harget zey, zogt er, m-

00:19:36.128 --> 00:19:47.836
mi- fun di fun di fun di oytomobiln, zogt er, fun di fun di oyf di, m'varft zey in di vagones, zogt er, s'nokh etlekhe froyen mitgeforn vos hobn gegebn di kleyne kinder, hot men zey oykh arayngeleygt dortn in di in dos, m'shrayt, m'veynt, zogt er, altsding, zog ikh im,

00:19:47.877 --> 00:19:50.065
vu? UNK nokh dem

00:19:50.475 --> 00:19:54.615
bay nakht, a zeyger tsen, elf, hot men aroysgefirt di ba- di kranke oykh.

00:19:54.615 --> 00:19:55.836
mit di kinder tsuzamen.

00:19:57.343 --> 00:19:59.429
zenen mir geven dortn tsvey teg oyfn besoylem.

00:20:00.128 --> 00:20:02.569
zogt er, Khatske, zogt er, vi lang veln mir do lign?

00:20:02.710 --> 00:20:07.091
zogt er, ikh gey, zogt er, oyf Linkuva, zogt er, ober du, zogt er, gey zikh dayn veg.

00:20:10.489 --> 00:20:11.782
veys nisht, s'mir geven

00:20:13.155 --> 00:20:15.641
modne zeyer, vos heyst modne? shreklekh!

00:20:15.641 --> 00:20:17.199
ober s'iz nit opgeven tsi dos redt.

00:20:17.779 --> 00:20:18.819
zogt er,

00:20:20.428 --> 00:20:22.717
gey tsurik, zogt er, bay zikh in lager, vu du bist geven.

00:20:24.040 --> 00:20:26.582
zog ikh, Yanosk, oyb du nemst mir, zog ikh, mit mikh,

00:20:26.807 --> 00:20:30.210
ikh ken dir nit mitnemen. aleyn, zogt er, vel ikh mir gefinen, vos nit iz, zogt er, nor

00:20:30.233 --> 00:20:31.678
ober tsveyt iz shoyn andern.

