bin ikh aroysgegangen a zeyger tsvey bay nakht ven er iz aroysgegangen. iz men aroysgegangen fun besoylem un ikh bin gegangen

00:20:37.131 --> 00:20:39.255
tsvey teg bin ikh gegangen in Kontsan,

00:20:39.666 --> 00:20:43.237
in tsi- in in in fabrik, vu ikh bin geven, vu m'hot mir aroysgenumen.

00:20:44.712 --> 00:20:48.215
hot mir mayn shtetlsher, dortn geven a shuster, a guter, fun mayn shtetl,

00:20:48.272 --> 00:20:50.088
er iz for der krig gekumen lebn in

00:20:51.411 --> 00:20:52.670
in Sh- in Shavl.

00:20:52.913 --> 00:20:54.662
er hot nor geneyt nor naye zakhn.

00:20:56.440 --> 00:20:57.868
zogt er, Khatske, zogt er,

00:20:59.089 --> 00:21:00.756
zets zikh bay mir, zogt er,

00:21:00.756 --> 00:21:03.524
ikh hob, zogt er, azoy fil arbet, ikh ken nisht bavayzn, zogt er, dos tsu ton.

00:21:03.524 --> 00:21:07.447
helf mir, zogt er, shu- gey ikh dir oyslernen, zogt er, shusteray, un UNK, zogt er, forn in Shavl.

00:21:07.447 --> 00:21:08.397
azoy iz forgekumen.

00:21:08.421 --> 00:21:10.220
er hot mir oysgelernt shusteray,

00:21:10.902 --> 00:21:15.789
un ikh bin geblibn dortn mit im, un di daytshn hobn im aroysgefirt in Shavl er zol neyen naye shtivl.

00:21:16.318 --> 00:21:19.215
un ikh bin geblibn der shuster fun fun lager.

00:21:21.685 --> 00:21:23.957
iz geven, Shilanski Shavln,

00:21:24.385 --> 00:21:28.884
in Shavl, di familye Shilanski vos er di itst, er iz geven der der der onfirer fun Kneset.

00:21:29.464 --> 00:21:30.774
Beke Shilanski.

00:21:31.084 --> 00:21:32.057
in Izrael.

00:21:32.907 --> 00:21:33.863
iz er ge-

00:21:35.033 --> 00:21:38.582
ze'mir geven tsuzamen. hot genumen zayn froy, iz geven zeyer a gute mentsh, zogt er,

00:21:38.582 --> 00:21:39.634
kinderlekh, zogt er,

