ir laydt nokh azoy fil, zogt er, mir baytn, zogt er, di zakhn un ir zayt nokh, zogt er, a dos, zogt er. un m'flegt zey nokh heysn geyn arbetn in a tsveyter UNK fabrik.

00:21:47.790 --> 00:21:53.133
vayl in tsuker fabrik dos iz geven shreklekhe arbet, di lodn di burikes fun di vagones!

00:21:53.477 --> 00:21:56.542
dos iz geven UNK arbet un di daytshn zenen geshtanen mit di nagaykes.

00:21:56.768 --> 00:21:58.753
vayl zey hobn gedarft hobn di tsuker farn front.

00:22:00.852 --> 00:22:04.474
hot zi undz tsugetulet, ot di froy Shilanski iz zeyer a guter mentsh,

00:22:04.497 --> 00:22:06.296
zi hot gehat tsvey tekhter un tsvey zin.

00:22:06.319 --> 00:22:09.041
un der elterer yingl, der yingerer yingl, zogt zi,

00:22:09.041 --> 00:22:10.582
Khatskl, zogt zi,

00:22:11.230 --> 00:22:13.874
ikh hob farshtanen far vos zi hot mir tsugetulet.

00:22:14.925 --> 00:22:18.682
take zi iz geven take zeyer a guter mentsh, zi hot gedarft dem yingl zol zikh tsulernen tsu shusteray arbet.

00:22:19.262 --> 00:22:20.504
un ikh hob im take tsu-

00:22:19.296 --> 00:22:20.539
Berlen?

00:22:20.562 --> 00:22:27.677
nit Berlen, dos iz geven der elterer, der geven a yingerer, Luke, Leybke, iz geven a yingerer yingl, er iz itster oykh a groyser onfirer in Erets Yisroel.

